    "description": "spoon is a Bioconductor package that addresses the mean-variance relationship in spatially resolved transcriptomics data using empirical Bayes techniques. The software prioritizes spatially variable genes by removing technical bias introduced by log-transformation, leading to more accurate identification of genes that vary in a 2D space.",
